episodes.title: Inventory
episodes.plot: Vaibhav migrates to Kota to prepare for India's toughest college entrance examination. Does this late entrant stand a chance in the race?

episodes.title: Assembly Line
episodes.plot: Vaibhav is part of the pack but 'studying' isn't the only hurdle he faces. When Meena, Uday and Shivangi fail to help him, Jeetu volunteers. Will Jeetu be able to save Vaibhav from the horrors of mess-food, insomnia and constipation?

episodes.title: Optimization
episodes.plot: There may be several paths to manufacture a product. But are the processes followed utilizing the resources optimally? Is the path followed that of least resistance?

episodes.title: Shut Down
episodes.plot: What is a better strategy to attain a goal - An uninterrupted stride without any intermissions or one that consists of rejuvenating breaks? Vaibhav and Meena find their modes of recharging.

episodes.title: Overhaul
episodes.plot: How far can one go to ensure success? Vaibhav left his home once for the cause, will he be able to do the same again?
